data.description: Stunning 5-BR 3.5 BA home just a short 5-min drive from Piedmont Hospital! As you enter through the 2-story foyer, you'll be greeted by the spacious great room boasting beautiful wood floors & a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring ss appliances, granite counters, tile backsplash, tile floors, a pantry, breakfast bar, & breakfast area. The main level owner's suite is a true retreat with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, & a luxurious ensuite bathroom complete with a separate shower and whirlpool tub. Upstairs, you'll find 4 additional generously sized bedrooms. The oversized 5th bedroom boasts its own ensuite full bathroom, making it perfect for guests or as a secondary owner's suite, media room, or playroom. The 2-car garage w/epoxy flooring provides ample parking & storage space. Outside, the large level fenced-in backyard is an entertainer's dream, featuring a covered porch with a ceiling fan & a fire pit. Close to I-85, shopping and restaurants.
